      "id": "PopularPost234565",
      "post_content": "So happy to see it back in darksteel.  \n  \nAnd in a precon (Master Blaster).  \nGood precon, actually.  \n  \nGreat spell.  \nBrutal card, brutal art, brutal flavour text.  \nYou get this fanastic feel from any X damage spell, especially with 10+ lands, but fireball has this imagery, of just rolling through armies and detonating in an opponents face.  \nBoom.  \n  \nAlso, you get thhat lovely flashback to D&D days, where all problems (-dragons) could be solved by old reliable.  \n  \n4.5/5 ",
      "posted_by": "Sharu",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost234565\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">So happy to see it back in darksteel.<br/><br/>And in a precon (Master Blaster).<br/>Good precon, actually.<br/><br/>Great spell.<br/>Brutal card, brutal art, brutal flavour text.<br/>You get this fanastic feel from any X damage spell, especially with 10+ lands, but fireball has this imagery, of just rolling through armies and detonating in an opponents face.<br/>Boom.<br/><br/>Also, you get thhat lovely flashback to D&amp;D days, where all problems (-dragons) could be solved by old reliable.<br/><br/>4.5/5  </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '234565'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy80001\">Sharu</span>\r\n                                (3/24/2012 10:46:28 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClea